he planet, which we\ntake to be the size of the planet's magnetosphere, ranges from 1 to 40\nplanetary radii.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Nov 2010 17:14:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
