tion and also offers new opportunities to couple quantum systems\nof different natures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Nov 2010 10:23:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Nov 2010 11:31:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-24"}
